In this season you see country superstar Lila Mccann as kellie wyman.  You see cordell become a principal after a principal after his friend is murdered.  this season has alot of action.  The children of halloween is the only episode that I didn't like.  I would give this season a full 5 stars.

When you buy this, please remember that it is actually the Seventh Season according to many websites such as [...] (the reason for this is because the first season was actually seasons one and two). With that said, according to the episode list, we only have ONE more release left and the entire awesome show is out on dvd!!!!!

Anyway, this season isn't any exception to the others. It stars Chuck Norris as a Texas Ranger, and his partner Trivette. They go out and solve crimes. There are some interesting episodes for this release. I love the second part of The Wedding which feature Walker pulverizing criminals because they hurt his chick Alex. So Walker interviews people by first unplugging the camera system, then plugging it back in only to feature a bloody mess singing like a canary. Other great episodes include livegirls.now which features some of the show's ridiculous, unrealistic view of real life crimes.

This dvd season comes differently than the previous ones. If you bought the previous seasons, you got a box set, with each case listing episodes and one dvd. This season is just one standard size DVD box with dvds stacked together in a book like fashion and the episodes are listing on transparent tabs on each side of the case. This feels a bit rushed and it looks odd on the shelf with my other collections. So this is a big no-no in my opinion. Hopefully cbs won't go cheap on the next release.
I just can,t wait for them to be released on dvd. I love watching walker, texas ranger at work, home, and long rides.

walker texas ranger was good from the begining.  still you could tell there was still something missing from the show.  In the second half of the fourth season (5th really) the something was found.  Chuck Norris with his roll as walker texas ranger began to inspire kids of all ages to not only turn from drugs and alcohol, but to find faith in Jesus Christ.

  this continued throughout the series.  this is wht made Chuck Norris my hero.  He used his show to inspire kids to not only have faith in theirselves but also to have Jesus.

It seems like every season is better than the last. Now with only one remaining to be released (Season 7) I can't wait for that realise. Season 6 of Walker changed over to the multi-pack clam shell case which is being used by most of the CBS releases (Raw Hide, Untouchables, The Fugitive, Gomer Pyle U.S.M.C. among many others. This new packaging takes up half the space, which is good. The episodes are of the high quality we are used to from the prior releases. It is a must own, but considering Season 6 ends with a cliff hanger, let's hope season 7 is realised soon!

Walker, Texas Ranger - The Complete Sixth Season Once again, Chuck Norris as Walker, Texas Ranger delivers an action packed experience.
